http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/mumbai/Thomas-Cook-hires-Vishal-Suri-as-Kuoni-MD/article13984349.ece

Thomas Cook (India) Ltd, a travel and travel-related financial services company, announced the appointment of Vishal Suri as managing director of Kuoni Travel (India) Pvt Ltd, effective January 4, following the exit of Rajeev Wagle.Prior to the appointment, Mr Suri headed the outbound portfolio as chief executive officer-tour operating, Kuoni India. Mr Suri has over 22 years of experience across consumer-centric industries like telecom, Internet, and office automation, Madhavan Menon, chairman and managing director, Thomas Cook (India) Ltd., said in a statement.